oai_dc:dc.dc:title: "Kissing Oak"
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: unknown
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: "Kissing Oak" between Johnson Bible College and Chapman Highway, on Kimberlin Heights Road, Knox County TN. Mr. and Mrs. Ashley Johnson kissing near the tree. Sign for Lowe - Hord Hardware on tree. The "Kissing Oak" was cut down in 1933 when Kimberlin Heights Road was improved.
